DEFINITELY.

03:20.504 --> 03:23.115
OK, SO THAT'S
EVERYTHING,
ISN'T IT?

03:23.115 --> 03:24.813
WELL,
WE KINDA COVERED
ALGEBRA, BIOLOGY--

03:24.813 --> 03:25.988
