NEXT TIME I PICK THE MOVIE,
YOU PICK THE RESTAURANT.

08:12.013 --> 08:13.580
WHAT, YOU DIDN'T
LIKE THE MOVIE?

08:13.580 --> 08:15.016
NO. I LOVED IT.

08:15.016 --> 08:16.757
I CAN'T REMEMBER
THE LAST TIME I HAD SO MUCH FUN

08:16.757 --> 08:18.454
WATCHING TEENAGERS
GET BLUDGEONED.

08:18.454 --> 08:21.152
