I SAW TONSILS.

08:45.307 --> 08:46.787
YOU JUST
THINK YOU DID.

08:46.787 --> 08:48.832
IT WAS PROBABLY
JUST A LOT OF...

08:48.832 --> 08:50.094
LIKE THAT.

08:50.094 --> 08:51.531
