REALLY BAD SHAPE.

10:23.797 --> 10:25.276
I-I'VE GOT, UM...

10:25.276 --> 10:26.800
SHE'S GOT A...

10:26.800 --> 10:28.149
A NOSEBLEED.

10:28.149 --> 10:30.586
OH, I THINK
IT'S STARTING AGAIN.

10:30.586 --> 10:32.109
IT'S REALLY BAD.

10:32.109 --> 10:33.545
