CLASSES GOING?

11:02.662 --> 11:04.620
FINE.
THEY'RE GOING FINE.

11:04.620 --> 11:07.144
AND YOU FOLKS ARE
BEGINNING TO GIVE
SOME THOUGHT

11:07.144 --> 11:08.668
TO A BIRTHING PLAN,
RIGHT?

11:08.668 --> 11:11.148
ALL I KNOW IS THAT
I WANT DRUGS.

11:11.148 --> 11:13.629
I WANT LOTS AND
LOTS OF DRUGS.

11:13.629 --> 11:16.545
