11:16.545 --> 11:19.156
I MEAN, CAN THEY HAVE
ANY ADVERSE EFFECTS
ON THE BABY?

11:19.156 --> 11:21.463
OH, YOU DON'T WANT ME
TO HAVE AN EPIDURAL?

11:21.463 --> 11:23.552
