IT'S NOT LIKE
WE'RE NOT GONNA

11:43.485 --> 11:44.834
FIND OUT
EVENTUALLY
ANYWAY.

11:44.834 --> 11:46.488
I JUST DON'T WANT
TO KNOW RIGHT NOW.

11:46.488 --> 11:48.664
WHAT DO YOU DO
IF ONE OF US
WANTS TO KNOW

11:48.664 --> 11:50.144
